OOC: OK, i'll remember that in the future.

:::Sideswipe/Ratchet/Torca/Sky Lynx:::

::Sideswipe destroys the missles and fires 2 missles and 25 shots at Double 
Punch::
~~~~~
::Ratchet destroys the missles, got hit by all the optic blasts, and gets hit 
by 3 ion disks.  He continues to bleed.  he fires 1 tusk missle at Double 
Punch, 1 at Manterror, and 15 shots from each gun at Injector::
~~~~~
::Torca got hit by one of the stinger missles and both the rapid bolts. He 
changes his gun configuration.  It was now a charge launcher.  he fired 1 
charge at Bumblebee and 1 charge at Sun Crusher::
~~~~~
::Sky Lynx looks for a target and spots Sixshot. He fires 2 missles from each 
of his two guns at Sixshot::

--part1_b4.f202486.2776ec29_boundary
